    -- `model`. The coordinate becomes the module-Container's id; an
    -- Allium::Module tag is applied. The use_aliases map (alias →
    -- imported-coord) drives cross-module reference resolution; when
    -- omitted, it is extracted from the AST's own `use` declarations.

